---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Tools | Kreativ Sound"
  description="Preset Mutator is the current Kreativ Sound browser tool for creating synth presets from audio, existing presets, or scratch ideas."
  canonical="https://kreativsound.com/tools/"
  activeNav="tools"
>
  <section class="card page-main product-page tools-page">
    <div class="stack">
      <div class="tools-hero tools-hero-grid">
        <div class="tools-hero-copy">
          <p class="product-kicker">Tools lab</p>
          <h1 class="page-title">Preset Mutator</h1>
          <p class="page-lead">Create Vital presets from scratch, mutate one preset, or analyze audio. From Scratch is the default starting point.</p>
        </div>
        <article class="product-panel product-panel-modern product-panel-accent tools-hero-panel">
          <p class="product-section-kicker">Current direction</p>
          <h2>One tool, three creation paths</h2>
          <p>One local-first app, three Vital workflows. Serum 2 and Pigments 7 support comes after the Vital workflow is solid.</p>
        </article>
      </div>

      <div class="product-panel-grid product-tool-grid product-tool-grid-single">
        <section class="product-panel product-tool-card product-tool-card-coming-soon product-panel-modern product-panel-accent">
          <span class="product-tool-flow">Audio -&gt; synth preset</span>
          <img class="product-tool-mark" src="/apps/preset-mutator/ui/preset-mutator-mark.svg" width="128" height="128" alt="Preset Mutator logo" />
          <h2>Preset Mutator</h2>
          <p>Create from scratch, mutate one existing Vital preset, or analyze a short sound. Vital export is live now, with Serum 2 and Pigments 7 planned as expansion targets.</p>
          <p class="product-tool-supporting">Best for quick sound-design sketches: pads, plucks, bass notes, drones, and textures that can become playable preset ideas.</p>
          <div class="product-actions">
            <a class="button primary" href="/apps/preset-mutator/ui/">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-wand-magic-sparkles" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              Open Preset Mutator
            </a>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>

      <section class="product-panel product-panel-summary product-panel-modern">
        <h2>Current tools strategy</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Preset Mutator is the main Kreativ Sound browser tool.</li>
          <li>From Scratch creates Vital starts without a source file.</li>
          <li>Mutate Preset loads one `.vital` preset and creates related variations.</li>
          <li>Audio to Preset analyzes one short source sound locally.</li>
          <li>Vital export is live first. Serum 2 and Pigments 7 support are planned next synth targets.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="product-panel-grid tools-mode-grid" aria-label="Preset Mutator modes">
        <article class="product-panel product-panel-modern product-panel-accent">
          <p class="product-section-kicker">Default path</p>
          <h2>From Scratch</h2>
          <p>Generate a new Vital preset direction from a simple intent instead of starting from a source file.</p>
          <div class="product-actions">
            <a class="button secondary" href="/apps/preset-mutator/ui/">Open From Scratch</a>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="product-panel product-panel-modern">
          <p class="product-section-kicker">Preset source</p>
          <h2>Mutate Preset</h2>
          <p>Load one Vital preset and push it into related variations without losing the original sound identity.</p>
          <div class="product-actions">
            <a class="button secondary" href="/apps/preset-mutator/ui/mutate/">Open Mutate Preset</a>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="product-panel product-panel-modern">
          <p class="product-section-kicker">Audio source</p>
          <h2>Audio to Preset</h2>
          <p>Use one short source sound, analyze it locally, and generate Vital preset directions you can refine.</p>
          <div class="product-actions">
            <a class="button secondary" href="/apps/preset-mutator/ui/audio/">Open Audio to Preset</a>
          </div>
        </article>
      </section>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
